 there, the waist should be a slot you have a high mana giving item on anyhow.  You don't need a 35kpp 10ac haste belt.<br><br>Warriors, monks, rangers, rogues, shadowknights, and paladins (in no particular order) are the only ones with a LEGITMATE claim to use this belt.  Anyone who disagrees, doesn't know their ass from their elbow.<br><br>(On a related note, if this belt or anything like it is merited on a raid, anyone selling merit loot before they have anything "better" should be deguilded immediately and blackballed)</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
